  "title": "Product Engineer (West) - Up to $3500",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>· Conduct research to understand user needs, market trends, and product requirements.</p><p>· R&D and/or source for new products for company to add to its product line.</p><p>· Develop detailed mechanical designs, including drawings, models, and specifications.</p><p>· Collaborate with engineers to ensure designs meet technical requirements and performance standards.</p><p>· Select appropriate materials and manufacturing processes for product designs.</p><p>· Assist in the build and test of prototypes to validate design concepts and functionality.</p><p>· Analyse test results and refine designs to address any issues or improve performance.</p><p>· Work closely with cross-functional teams, including industrial designers, electrical engineers, and manufacturing teams, to bring products from concept to production.</p><p>· Participate in design reviews, provide feedback, and make necessary adjustments based on input from stakeholders.</p><p>· Communicate effectively with suppliers and vendors to ensure the feasibility and cost-effectiveness of designs.</p><p>· Create and maintain detailed documentation of designs, including specifications, calculations, catalogues and revisions.</p><p>· Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Minimum Diploma in Electrical Engineering, Industrial Design, or a related field.</p><p>· At least 2 years of experience in mechanical product design.</p><p>· Proficiency in CAD software (e.g., SolidWorks, AutoCAD).</p><p>· Strong knowledge of product development processes, materials, and manufacturing processes.</p><p>· Ability to work collaboratively in a team environment and communicate effectively.<br /><br /><strong></strong><br /><strong>Interested and suitable candidate kindly click quick apply. Resume will be forwarded to Stepfan Soon Yit</strong></p><p><strong>We regret that only suitable candidate will be notified.</strong></p><p><strong>GEMS Recruit/EA License : 23C1459</strong></p><p><strong>EA Personnel No : R24120893 (Stepfan Soon Yit)</strong></p>",
